span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">改判誤殺罪成，判刑監禁8年</span></strong></span>。他於05年獲釋後被即時遣返回中國大陸，於2011年成功申請單程證再來香港，引起香港社會嘩然和部份人士要求改革單程證制度。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好玩火。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[Be fire, my foe] 攬炒戰術？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nx22GfM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnx22GfM.png&h=e601a00b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwkf1fN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjwkf1fN.png&h=c4b0c622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xW81WO5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxW81WO5.png&h=e9e3f844&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dvebqS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dvebqS</a>"},{"pid":"6c8b9a6e55594fdd65eaa1e4045de25ba165aea1","tid":1404670,"uid":270912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:36:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4a3414ba72855da3387ad46add7e8f0c86bbca1","tid":1404670,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復漁業，活捉鮮魚</span></strong></em></div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnQoqAi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnQoqAi.gif&h=43f17f63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5050219d54dfca3b1a9d88511e912c3e6a48f53","tid":1404670,"uid":270912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad6e8463fd8bb0ebb50407c97c2c15926ce91d01","tid":1404670,"uid":270912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d06941c55590d3a4e5184f4e66e2d86695752cd1","tid":1404670,